The race of orcs is one of a short, fierce people, who have had to 
struggle constantly to make their place in the world.  They are 
almost universally disliked by others, even though their society is 
nearly as advanced as many other peoples'.  They are a strong and 
sturdy race, which is one of the primary reasons they have survived.

Orcs do slightly more damage in combat than the other races.
 
Orcs cannot join the following guilds:  Bard, Charlatan, Cleric of Mitra, 
Mage, Swashbuckler, Paladin.
